Amazon SageMaker Features — Pinoy Version 🇵🇭
  
  Core Concept
  
  │ SageMaker = Complete kitchen for Machine Learning. Lahat ng kailangan mo para
  mag-train at mag-deploy ng AI model, nandito na — data prep, training, deployment,
  monitoring. Hindi mo na kailangang mag-setup ng sarili mong GPU servers.
  
  ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  
  📋 Lahat ng Features
  
  1. SageMaker Studio
  
  Ano to: Workspace/IDE mo para sa ML — parang VS Code pero para sa data science.
  Pinoy analogy: Parang opisina mo na kumpleto na — may desk, computer, whiteboard, lahat
  nandun na.
  
  2. SageMaker Notebooks
  
  Ano to: Jupyter notebooks na naka-host sa cloud. Pwede ka mag-experiment at mag-code
  dito.
  Pinoy analogy: Parang scratch paper mo habang nag-e-experiment ka ng recipe bago lutuin
  for real.
  
  3. Training Jobs
  
  Ano to: Dito ka mag-t-train ng model. Pipili ka ng instance type (CPU o GPU), tapos AWS
  ang mag-provision at mag-run.
  Pinoy analogy: Parang nag-rent ka ng commercial kitchen — malaki, may industrial oven,
  tapos pag tapos ka na magluto, ibabalik mo na. Bayad ka lang sa oras na ginamit mo.
  
  4. Built-in Algorithms
  
  Ano to: Pre-made ML algorithms na ready to use — XGBoost, Linear Learner, Image
  Classification, etc.
  Pinoy analogy: Parang instant mix — hindi mo na kailangang gumawa ng recipe from
  scratch. May ready-made na, i-mix mo lang sa data mo.
  
